{"tid":1505471,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下跪唔係因為懦弱，而係因為勇氣","createTime":"2019-08-25T14:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:13:58.000Z","uid":120629,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d852eea3035c98bad3863a459df80d63394a6069","tid":1505471,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:19:23.000Z","msg":"一個手無寸鐵既老人<br />\n面對住一群失控既猛獸<br />\n被真槍實彈指嚇<br />\n佢冇選擇置身事外<br />\n相反係用血肉之軀試圖擋住猛獸<br />\n佢甚至放棄所謂既尊嚴去下跪<br />\n試圖喚醒猛獸既良知<br />\n懦弱既人一早就走左，但佢冇<br />\n因為佢有無比既勇氣，願意為香港既和平作出犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n如果係你地<br />\n又有幾多人對住真槍實彈之下<br />\n仍能奮不顧身?"},{"pid":"f94edc57ee49d093a20b9f0552d5ee6ecc57672e","tid":1505471,"uid":148824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"醒啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對敵人仁慈=對自己殘忍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff52609a7d2f9e61c71d02ef824435eca99487b2","tid":1505471,"uid":210817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:20:50.000Z","msg":"人類的偉大就是勇氣的偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce25e819ed36e5472ca2da2f78f002d69d4f769","tid":1505471,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e00352e546f2cf8fef74a1fed641e82c56fdc95","tid":1505471,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link